<p class="text-lg">{!! translate('USD Coin (USDC) is a fully reserved, dollar-pegged stablecoin that provides transparency, liquidity, and stability on Coinbase\'s Base blockchain. Issued by Circle, USDC is widely used across the crypto ecosystem for payments, trading, lending, and earning yield. On Base, it combines the benefits of fast, low-cost transactions with the trustworthiness of a regulated stablecoin.') !!}</p>
<p class="text-lg mt-5">{!! translate('USDC is critical for decentralized finance (DeFi) users who want to hedge against volatility without exiting the blockchain. It enables seamless swaps, yield farming, and liquidity provision across Base-native protocols. As a bridge between traditional finance and the decentralized world, USDC is essential for institutions and retail users alike.') !!}</p>
<p class="text-lg mt-5">{!! translate('The integration of USDC on Base supports its mission of building a user-friendly, scalable crypto economy. Its programmability, auditability, and compatibility with smart contracts make it an essential building block for developers and users engaging with Web3 products on Base.') !!}</p>
